videos.description: Jordan McLaughlin comes down with the defensive board and launches a perfect alley-oop pass to Chimezie Metu for the jam.
videos.headline: Trojans' McLaughlin tosses half-court alley-oop to Metu

videos.description: Elijah Stewart reaches in and pokes the ball free then finds Shaqquan Aaron ahead of the pack for the slam.
videos.headline: Stewart robbery leads to Aaron slam for the Trojans

videos.description: Aaron Holiday drives the lane and somehow finds a way to drop the layup for his 30th points of the night.
videos.headline: Holiday reaches 30 points with circus layup
